Symbol.Script_3D:
sectDepth = sectDepth/1000 sectThick = sectThick/1000 Rad = sectThick sectLip = sectLip/1000 TopWidth = TopWidth/1000 BottomWidth = BottomWidth/1000
PEN gs_cont_pen MATERIAL col_mat if gs_shadow=0 then SHADOW off else SHADOW on endif
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then end
!---------Cutplanes modz = zzyzx unIDCut = 100
if bCutPlanes Then
wsds = sqr(sectDepth^2 + (BottomWidth+TopWidth)^2)
!!!-------------------- Top Cutting If ABS(gs_cutang1_bot) > EPS OR ABS(gs_cutang2_bot) > EPS Then modz = modz+tan(60)* wsds/2
Rotz gs_cutdir_top addz zzyzx rotx 90
cutpoly 5, -wsds/2,tan(60)* wsds /2, wsds/2,tan(60)* wsds /2, wsds/2, tan(gs_cutang1_bot)* wsds /2, 0,0, -wsds/2, tan(gs_cutang2_bot)* wsds /2
del 3 endif
!!!-------------------- Bottom Cutting If ABS(gs_cutang3_bot) > EPS OR ABS(gs_cutang4_bot) > EPS Then modz = modz+tan(60)* wsds /2
Rotz gs_cutdir_but rotx 90
cutpoly 5, -wsds/2,-tan(60)* wsds /2, wsds/2,-tan(60)* wsds /2, wsds/2, tan(gs_cutang3_bot)* wsds /2, 0,0, -wsds/2, tan(gs_cutang4_bot)* wsds /2
del 2 addz -tan(60)*wsds/2 endif endif
!---------Cutplanes
RRadius=sectThick*2
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then PRISM_ 13,modz, sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, 15, sectThick/2, sectDepth/2-sectThick, 15, TopWidth-sectThick/2-sectThick, sectDepth/2-sectThick, 15, TopWidth-sectThick/2-sectThick, sectDepth/2-sectLip, 15, TopWidth-sectThick/2, sectDepth/2-sectLip, 15, TopWidth-sectThick/2, sectDepth/2, 15, -sectThick/2, sectDepth/2,15, -sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2+sectThick,15, -(BottomWidth-sectThick/2)+sectThick, -sectDepth/2+sectThick,15, -(BottomWidth-sectThick/2)+sectThick, -sectDepth/2+sectLip,15, -(BottomWidth-sectThick/2), -sectDepth/2+sectLip,15, -(BottomWidth-sectThick/2), -sectDepth/2,15, sectThick/2, -sectDepth/2, -1
endif if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then
!!! Curved Resolution S=90/gs_resol FOR k=0 TO 90 STEP S PUT -sectThick/2-Rad+(Rad+sectThick)*sin(k),-sectDepth/2+sectThick+Rad-(Rad+sectThick)*cos(k),79 NEXT k FOR k=90 TO 180 STEP S PUT sectThick/2+Rad-Rad*sin(k),sectDepth/2-sectThick-Rad-Rad*cos(k),79 NEXT k FOR k=180 TO 270 STEP S PUT TopWidth-sectThick/2-sectThick-Rad-Rad*sin(k),sectDepth/2-sectThick-Rad-Rad*cos(k),79 NEXT k FOR k=270 TO 180 STEP -S PUT TopWidth-sectThick/2-sectThick-Rad-(Rad+sectThick)*sin(k),sectDepth/2-sectThick-Rad-(Rad+sectThick)*cos(k),79 NEXT k FOR k=180 TO 90 STEP -S PUT -sectThick/2+sectThick+Rad-(Rad+sectThick)*sin(k),sectDepth/2-sectThick-Rad-(Rad+sectThick)*cos(k),79 NEXT k FOR k=90 TO 0 STEP -S PUT -sectThick/2-Rad+(Rad)*sin(k),-sectDepth/2+sectThick+Rad-(Rad)*cos(k),79 NEXT k FOR k=0 TO -90 STEP -S PUT -(BottomWidth-sectThick/2)+sectThick+Rad+(Rad)*sin(k),-sectDepth/2+sectThick+Rad-(Rad)*cos(k),79 NEXT k FOR k=-90 TO 0 STEP S PUT -(BottomWidth-sectThick/2)+sectThick+Rad+(Rad+sectThick)*sin(k),-sectDepth/2+sectThick+Rad-(Rad+sectThick)*cos(k),79 NEXT k
PRISM_ 5+NSP/3,modz, GET(NSP/8), GET(NSP/7), GET(NSP/6), TopWidth-sectThick/2-sectThick, sectDepth/2-sectLip, 15, TopWidth-sectThick/2, sectDepth/2-sectLip, 15, GET(NSP/5), GET(NSP/4), GET(NSP/3), GET(NSP/2), -(BottomWidth-sectThick/2)+sectThick, -sectDepth/2+sectLip,15, -(BottomWidth-sectThick/2), -sectDepth/2+sectLip,15, GET(NSP), -sectThick/2-Rad, -sectDepth/2, -1
endif
!---------Cutplanes if bCutPlanes Then If ABS(gs_cutang1_bot) > EPS OR ABS(gs_cutang2_bot) > EPS then cutend
If ABS(gs_cutang3_bot) > EPS OR ABS(gs_cutang4_bot) > EPS then del 1 cutend endif endif !---------Cutplanes
unID=1 HOTSPOT 0,0,0, unID, ZZYZX, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,0,-1, unID, ZZYZX, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,0,ZZYZX, unID, ZZYZX, 2 : unID=unID+1
!---------Bottom Hotspots rotx 90 if iCutModeColBottom = CUTMODE_ALONG_X then HOTSPOT TopWidth-sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang3_bot)* sectDepth/2, -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -BottomWidth+sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang4_bot)* sectDepth/2, sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1
HOTSPOT TopWidth-sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang3_bot)* (sectDepth/2-sectLip), -sectDepth/2+sectLip, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -BottomWidth+sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang4_bot)* (sectDepth/2-sectLip), sectDepth/2-sectLip, unID : unID = unID+1
HPxMiddleBot = sectDepth cutAngleHSBot1 = gs_cutang3_bot cutAngleHSBot3 = gs_cutang4_bot else HOTSPOT TopWidth-sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang3_bot)* (TopWidth-sectThick/2), -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -BottomWidth+sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang4_bot)* (BottomWidth-sectThick/2), sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1
HOTSPOT TopWidth-sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang3_bot)* (TopWidth-sectThick/2), -sectDepth/2+sectLip, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -BottomWidth+sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang4_bot)* (BottomWidth-sectThick/2), sectDepth/2-sectLip, unID : unID = unID+1
HPxMiddleBot = sectThick cutAngleHSBot1 = gs_cutang4_bot cutAngleHSBot3 = gs_cutang3_bot endif
HOTSPOT sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHSBot3)* HPxMiddleBot/2, sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHSBot1)* HPxMiddleBot/2, -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 del 1
!---------Top Hotspots addz zzyzx rotx 90
if iCutModeColTop = CUTMODE_ALONG_X then HOTSPOT TopWidth-sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang1_bot)* sectDepth/2, -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -BottomWidth+sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang2_bot)* sectDepth/2, sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1
HOTSPOT TopWidth-sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang1_bot)* (sectDepth/2-sectLip), -sectDepth/2+sectLip, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -BottomWidth+sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang2_bot)* (sectDepth/2-sectLip), sectDepth/2-sectLip, unID : unID = unID+1
HPxMiddle = sectDepth cutAngleHS1 = gs_cutang1_bot cutAngleHS3 = gs_cutang2_bot else HOTSPOT TopWidth-sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang1_bot)* (TopWidth-sectThick/2), -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -BottomWidth+sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang2_bot)* (BottomWidth-sectThick/2), sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1
HOTSPOT TopWidth-sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang1_bot)* (TopWidth-sectThick/2), -sectDepth/2+sectLip, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -BottomWidth+sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(gs_cutang2_bot)* (BottomWidth-sectThick/2), sectDepth/2-sectLip, unID : unID = unID+1
HPxMiddle = sectThick cutAngleHS1 = gs_cutang2_bot cutAngleHS3 = gs_cutang1_bot endif
HOTSPOT sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHS3)* HPxMiddle/2, sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -sectThick/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHS1)* HPxMiddle/2, -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 del 2
end
